Editor’s note: This livestream has ended. You may watch the recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The Economic Freedom Fighters (EFF) hosted a Press Conference on Thursday at their headquarters in Braamfontein. The briefing was addressed by EFF commander in chief Julius Malema and is also expected to be addressed by other officials. Malema called for Terence Nombembe to recuse himself from Judge Raymond Zondo's state capture enquiry, as he claimed that Nombembe had a conflict of interest. eNCA